The paper deals with a problem related to graph drawing, specifically the drawing of complete graphs with slope constraints. This falls under computational geometry (cs.CG) and graph theory (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the complexity of the problem, which is a common theme in computational complexity (cs.CC) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). Finally, the paper presents an algorithm for solving the problem, which could be of interest to researchers in algorithmic game theory (cs.GT).
